author: Odeinoichus
title: Rowr. I'm a Dinosaur!
review:
Set #41775 Dinosaur Unikitty: This cute variant from the blind bag range uses all green parts for Unikitty's torso and tail and other parts. Her tail has been printed with scales and spikes, her torso is equally covered in scales with a cute little light-green chest detail on the front of the bridge brick and her face shows Unikitty looking out from inside a Dinosaur head mask. Complete with visible teeth, eyes and nostrils.

This is a strong offering and one I'm sure a lot of fans were interested in. She's super cute and the parts are super fun. She's Super Recommended.
